title: Add a dataset to curatedAdipoChIP
body:
Hello, 
I would like to add a dataset to the curatedAdipoChIP but I don't know how to do it. 
I have a dataset (affymetrix) with 3 samples at 12 days of differentiation and 3 others from a co-culture. 
Could you please help me to do that? 

Thank you 

Nicolas
